data.description: This spacious condo offers the perfect blend of convenience, sophistication, and comfort, ensuring an elevated lifestyle. Situated just minutes away from major traffic arteries, this home ensures effortless commuting to any destination, allowing you to spend less time in traffic and more time enjoying the things you love. Take a moment to appreciate the high ceilings, with popcorn ceilings removed, that amplify the sense of space and openness, creating a welcoming atmosphere for you and your guests. The updated kitchen offers a pleasant experience, featuring sleek black stainless appliances that combine style with functionality including double ovens and a warming drawer. Notice that every single light fixture has been replaced. Say goodbye to carpet maintenance with renovated floors that offer easy upkeep and modern elegance. Efficiency meets elegance with renovated high-quality windows that not only enhance the aesthetic appeal of the home but also contribute to energy conservation. Luxurious custom-made wood plantation shutters add a touch of sophistication, elevating the ambiance of this beautiful residence. Step outside to the cozy patio-where you can savor your morning coffee or unwind with evening beverages. With an oversized 2-car garage, convenience seamlessly integrates with functionality, providing ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. For your comfort this property boasts a water softener system, and a security system! The primary room, conveniently located on the main floor, offers a spacious and luminous owner's suite, an updated bathroom, and a retreat that is spacious and bright. Gather around the gas-log fireplace, the heart of the home, where cherished memories are made and warmth permeates every corner. Upstairs, you'll discover the remaining two guest bedrooms and a full bathroom. A versatile loft/flex area awaits, perfect for creating your ideal home office or TV area, providing the flexibility to tailor the space to suit your lifestyle. HOA dues include water and trash, along with upkeep of all common areas.  Enjoy the beautiful community pool during the San Antonio summers. Welcome Home!
